\c 14
\s Jehovha anodana Israeri kuti adzokere kwaari
\p
\v 1 Dzoka, haiwa Israeri, kuna Jehovha Mwari wako, nokuti wakagumburwa nechitadzo chako.
\v 2 Tora mashoko \add awa\add* pamwe newe ugodzokera kuna Jehovha uti kwaari: Bvisa uipi hwese mugo\add ti\add*gamuchira nenyasha, naizvozvo ticharipa hando dzemiromo yedu.
\v 3 Asiriya havangatiponesi; haangatasvi mabhiza, uye hatichazotizve kubasa remaoko edu: \add Muri\add* vamwari vedu; nokuti mamuri nherera dzinowana nyasha.
\p
\v 4 Ndichaporesa kudzokera shure kwavo, ndichavada pachena; nokuti kutsamwa kwangu kwabviswa kwaari.
\v 5 Ndichava sedova kuna Israeri, achatunga seruva, uye achatanda midzi yake seRebhanoni.
\v 6 Matavi ake achatanda, uye kubwinya kwake kuchava semuti wemuorivhi, nemunhuhwi wake seRebhanoni.
\v 7 Vanogara mumumvuri wake vachadzoka, vachavandudzika \add se\add*zviyo, nekutunga semuzambiringa; chirangaridzo chake sewaini yeRebhanoni.
\v 8 Efuremu, ndichinei nezvifananidzo? Ini ndaka\add mu\add*pindura, ndakamucherekedza, ndikava semuti wemufiri munyoro, chibereko chako chinowanikwa kubva kwandiri.
\p
\v 9 Ndiani wakachenjera? Zvino achanzwisisa izvi. Wakangwara, zvino achazviziva, nokuti nzira dzaJehovha dzakarurama, uye vakarurama vachafamba madziri, asi vadariki vachagumburwa madziri.